Rows.contentTitle: Hop on Pop - Read & Learn - Dr. Seuss
Rows.descript:
4.0/en/"An all-new, iOS-only, paid app of the Dr. Seuss favorite, Hop on Pop. This app contains premium features, like Common Core aligned learning activities, animations, reading statistics, and more.

- A hidden activity on every page connects young readers to story content through Common Core aligned educational activities that help readers practice consonant sorting and matching, uppercase and lowercase recognition, and more. Once found, activities can be played again and again via the book's main menu."
